column3: Green-Bell-Pepper
column4: green_bell_pepper_iconic|There are a variety of colors of peppers. The most common ones are green, yellow, orange, red and white. column3: Orange-Bell-Pepper

column3: Sweet-Potato
column4: sweet_potato_iconic|Sweet potatoes are oblong, irregularly shaped tubers, often slightly larger than regular potatoes. The peel is light brown or red. column3: red_beet_iconic|Red beets has an earthy and sweet taste and is often eaten on the side, either cooked or preserved, for example, to pölsa, pyttipanna or steak Lindström.
